lead_paragraph: Striker Zlatan Ibrahimovic has leapt to the defence of club mate Wayne Rooney, saying the Manchester United captain is a "perfect" player who does not get enough respect in England.

headline.print_headline: 'Perfect' Rooney Deserves More Respect, Says Ibrahimovic
headline.main: 'Perfect' Rooney Deserves More Respect, Says Ibrahimovic
